description:
Any musician has learned this hard lesson. For Matthew Garrison (son of Jimmy Garrison), it was when he was 17, while studying with bass legend Dave Holland, which was set up by Matt’s godfather, Jack DeJohnette, who Matt now performs with at SFJAZZ to close out this week's #ColtraneLegacy series on September 24. Family connections!

More info: http://bit.ly/2hdEES3
